/* eslint-disable template-curly-spacing */
 
import { css } from "emotion";
 
// import {unitMath,applyUnitIfRequired} from "../../../utils/css-utils";
import styleMemoize from "../../../utils/style-memoize";
import flaggedStyles from "../../../utils/flagged-styles";
// import {unitMath} from "../../utils/css-utils";
import getLabelVars from "./label.var";
 
 
export default styleMemoize(function (flags = []/*, variation, size*/) {
 
  const labelVars = getLabelVars();
 
  const {
    iconDistance,
    cornerIconLeftOffset,
    cornerIconSize,
    cornerIconTopOffset
  } = labelVars;
 
  return flaggedStyles("label-icon", flags, {
 
    _: () => (css`
 
      width: auto;
      margin: 0em ${iconDistance} 0em 0em;
 
    `),
 
    // /* Removable label */
    // .ui.label > .close.icon,
    // .ui.label > .delete.icon {
    //   cursor: pointer;
    //   margin-right: 0em;
    //   margin-left: @deleteMargin;
    //   font-size: @deleteSize;
    //   opacity: @deleteOpacity;
    //   transition: @deleteTransition;
    // }
    // .ui.label > .delete.icon:hover {
    //   opacity: 1;
    // }
 
    loading: ()=>(css`
      & svg {
        display:none;
      }
    `),
 
    corner: ()=>(css`
 
      cursor: default;
      position: relative;
      top: ${cornerIconTopOffset};
      left: ${cornerIconLeftOffset};
      font-size: ${cornerIconSize};
      margin: "0em";
    
    `),
    
    "corner,left": ()=>(css`
      
      left: -${cornerIconLeftOffset};
 
    `),
 
  });
 
});
